'''The Tolkien Art of the Brothers Hildebrandt 2004 Calendar''' was produced by Ronnie Sellers Productions, Inc. and contains illustrations by the [[Brothers Hildebrandt]].

* ISBN 1-56906-683-3
* Dimensions: 12 x 12 inches
* Stapled
* Punched hanging hole
* Shrink-wrapped
